    This was the first time that the [graph](/Grapheme) 礻升 had been attested in [oracle bone inscriptions](/Oracle_bone_script). Wang translated the sentence as: "Prognostication on the day *dingwei*: if the king performs the *sheng* sacrifice, will it benefit Ancestor Wu?" The newly found [graph](/Grapheme) was tentatively assigned the same modern reading as the phonetic component 升.
